caption: <SOS>This photo is taken outside on a sunny day. A group of people are walking on a sidewalk in front of a brick building. Two carted vehicles are parked next to the buildings. Buildings can be seen in the background behind the vehicles. A blue sky is overcast and cloudless.<EOS>

Across the street from the bus is a building with a red brick facade.  Two people are walking down the sidewalk on the left side of the photo.<EOS>
